      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey just had a question about my warfarin. ive been on 5mg for a while now and honestly im feeling great, like super healthy. i was thinking since im doing so well i could probably just drop down to 2mg a day to keep it steady? feels like a lot of medicine for how good i feel lately.",
